title: Suicide bombers target Uganda's capital Kampala
content: At least three people are killed in the blasts near parliament and the city's police HQ.

title: China warns US about 'playing with fire' on Taiwan
content: Xi Jinping and Joe Biden hold substantial talks but exchange sharp words on Taiwan.

title: Polish forces tear-gas migrants at Belarus border
content: Poland's defence ministry says migrants were throwing stones and trying to destroy a border fence.

title: France clears major migrant camp amid UK tensions
content: About 1,500 people are evacuated near Dunkirk, as the UK and France vow to tackle illegal migration.

title: Russian anti-satellite missile test sparks outrage
content: The US says Russia "recklessly" destroyed a satellite, endangering astronauts in space.

title: Australian family rescued after days in outback
content: The couple and two children became stranded when their campervan got bogged down in mud.

title: Alfa make Zhou China's first F1 driver
content: Guanyu Zhou becomes Formula 1's first Chinese driver after signing to race for Alfa Romeo in 2022.
